### 🟢 GET - Obtener todos los clientes
GET http://localhost:8081/clientes


### 🟢 POST - Crear nuevo cliente
POST http://localhost:8081/clientes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Jeremy Vega",
  "rut": "19658977-5",
  "correo": "jere4.@example.com",
  "telefono": "+569123456789",
  "region_comuna": "Santiago"
}


### 🟡 PATCH - Actualizar cliente con ID X
### Para conservar los mismos datos poner ""
PATCH http://localhost:8081/clientes/15
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "",
  "rut": "",
  "correo": "",
  "telefono": "",
  "region_comuna": ""
}

### 🟡 DELETE - Borrar cliente con ID X
DELETE http://localhost:8081/clientes/12

